# Fingerprint Sensor Hardware Setup (R305/ZFM-20 Example)

## Components
- R305 / ZFM-20 Fingerprint Sensor
- Arduino Uno / Mega
- Jumper Wires

## Pin Connections (R305 to Arduino UNO)
| Fingerprint Pin | Arduino UNO Pin |
|-----------------|-----------------|
| VCC             | 5V              |
| GND             | GND             |
| TX              | D2              |
| RX              | D3              |

## Notes
- Use `Adafruit Fingerprint` library in Arduino IDE.
- Enroll and verify fingerprints from Arduino, send verification result to C program.
